    <h1>Structured Data</h1>
    <p class="description">Machine-readable code added to web pages to explicitly communicate content meaning to search engines. Powers <strong>rich results, AI citations, and Knowledge Graph entries</strong> — the layer between your words and what search engines understand them to mean.</p>
